      <title>美国银行高管预计特朗普将放松规则，促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-bank-executives-expect-trump-ease-rules-fuel-growth-2024-12-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[行业高管周三在纽约举行的路透社 NEXT 会议的一个小组讨论会上表示，预计当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将采取有利于增长的政策，放宽美国银行业和信用卡监管，同时刺激交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-bank-executives-expect-trump-ease-rules-fuel-growth-2024-12-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 15:59:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
