      <title>汇丰银行对求职银行家歧视指控上诉失败</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-loses-appeal-over-job-seeking-bankers-discrimination-claim-2024-12-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行周三对伦敦法院恢复一名高级银行家的诉讼的判决提出上诉，该诉讼称，汇丰银行在 2018 年未能聘用她担任高级销售职位时对她进行了迫害和歧视。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-loses-appeal-over-job-seeking-bankers-discrimination-claim-2024-12-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Dec 2024 15:04:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
